title: Musk Inc.? Billionaire combines his rocket and AI businesses before an expected IPO this year
description: NEW YORK (AP) — Elon Musk is joining his space exploration and artificial intelligence ventures into a single company before what's expected to be a massive initial public offering for the business later this year.
